    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the tetromino game you've always wanted. Implement advanced techniques not found in any other tetromino game. Use zig-zag, zipper, x-ray techniques, and multiplayer tactics to clear 5-10 lines at a time. Play solo or go nuclear with up to four players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to learn. Hard to master. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-ray, zipper, zig-zag features not found in any other tetromino game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combines classic tetromino gameplay with chaining techniques.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to four friends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274700/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.poster.avif?t=1728186043\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274700/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.webm?t=1728186043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274700/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.mp4?t=1728186043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team up with with friends to build faster and make larger chains.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274700/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.poster.avif?t=1728186043\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274700/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.webm?t=1728186043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s